title: Kendall Jenner practically nude in Calvin Klein ads | The
text:
KENDALL Jenner’s reign as the darling of the fashion world continues, as pictures of her starring in an advertisement for Calvin Klein are released.
In a series of two images on her Instagram account, Jenner is seen in, well, nothing but her Calvin’s — and she looks incredible.
Kendall for Calvin Klein (Frame content direct link: http://instagram.com/p/44ERYbjo7L/embed .)
Kendall for Calvin Klein (Frame content direct link: http://instagram.com/p/44Zv63Do09/embed .)
Calvin Klein’s latest campaign is entitled ‘The Original Sexy’, and also features Joan Smalls, Isabeli Fontana and Edita Vilkeviciute.
Jenner landed her first campaign for Calvin Klein earlier this year, and is showing no signs of ending the partnership anytime soon. She told WWD that working with the brand is “super fun. Every girl loves posing in her underwear. It’s always fun to do that.”
It’s a far cry from the top-to-toe look she rocked at the Chanel show as part of Paris Fashion Week two days ago, but the 19-year-old can clearly pull off any look she’s given — and it’s all part of her charm.
Kendall Jenner walks the runway for Chanel’s during Haute Couture Fall/Winter 2015/2016 collection. Source: Getty Images
Originally published as Kendall Jenner near-nude for Calvin Klein
